          <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
          <p class="lead">This Privacy Policy explains how HireHelper.ai collects, uses, stores, and protects personal information submitted through the public website, including contact forms, project inquiry forms, cookies, and website analytics.</p>
          <div class="legal-note">This page should be reviewed by legal counsel before publication.</div>
