    <section class="section">
      <div class="container narrow">
        <section class="legal-card" data-reveal><h2>Information we collect</h2><p>HireHelper.ai may collect information you provide directly, including your name, work email, company name, website, inquiry topic, and any project details or message content you submit through public forms.</p></section><section class="legal-card" data-reveal><h2>Information collected automatically</h2><p>Like most websites, HireHelper.ai may collect certain technical information automatically, including browser type, device type, pages viewed, referral source, approximate location based on IP address, and interactions with website pages. This information may be collected through cookies, analytics tools, or similar technologies.</p></section><section class="legal-card" data-reveal><h2>How we use information</h2><p>HireHelper.ai uses the information collected through the public website to review inquiries, respond to messages, evaluate potential project fit, improve website performance, understand website usage, maintain security, and support business operations.</p></section><section class="legal-card" data-reveal><h2>Legal basis and consent</h2><p>Where required by applicable law, HireHelper.ai processes personal information based on consent, legitimate interest, legal obligation, or the need to take steps requested before a potential business relationship begins.</p></section><section class="legal-card" data-reveal><h2>How information may be shared</h2><p>HireHelper.ai may share information with trusted service providers who support website hosting, analytics, communications, storage, or operations, but only to the extent reasonably necessary for those services. HireHelper.ai does not sell personal information submitted through the public website.</p></section><section class="legal-card" data-reveal><h2>Data retention</h2><p>HireHelper.ai retains personal information only for as long as reasonably necessary to respond to inquiries, evaluate business opportunities, meet legal obligations, resolve disputes, or maintain security and business records.</p></section><section class="legal-card" data-reveal><h2>Your rights</h2><p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to request access to your personal information, ask for correction, request deletion, object to certain processing, or request a copy of the information you provided. Requests can be sent to privacy@hirehelper.ai.</p></section><section class="legal-card" data-reveal><h2>Cookies and analytics</h2><p>HireHelper.ai may use cookies and similar technologies to understand website traffic, improve performance, remember preferences, and support security. You may be able to control certain cookie settings through your browser.</p></section><section class="legal-card" data-reveal><h2>Data security</h2><p>HireHelper.ai takes reasonable administrative, technical, and organizational measures to help protect personal information submitted through the public website. No system can guarantee absolute security.</p></section><section class="legal-card" data-reveal><h2>Children's privacy</h2><p>The public website is not directed to children, and HireHelper.ai does not knowingly collect personal information from children through the public site.</p></section><section class="legal-card" data-reveal><h2>Changes to this policy</h2><p>HireHelper.ai may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The current version will be published on this page with the most recent effective date.</p></section><section class="legal-card" data-reveal><h2>Contact</h2><p>For privacy questions or rights requests, contact: privacy@hirehelper.ai</p></section>
